import React from "react"; export default function StudentsList({ students, startEdit, deleteStudent }) { return (

ALL STUDENTS

{students.length === 0 ? (

No students in database.

) : (
{students.map((s) => (
{/* Main content area */}

{s.name}

Roll: {s.rollno}

{/* Email with word break to prevent overflow */}
Email: {s.email}
{s.phone && (
Phone: {s.phone}
)}
SIG: {s.sig}
Role: {s.role}
{/* Meta info at the bottom of the content section */}
ID: {/* ID is truncated with an ellipsis if it's too long */} {s._id}
{s.createdAt && (
Created: {new Date(s.createdAt).toLocaleDateString()}
)}
{/* Action buttons area, mt-auto pushes this to the bottom */}
{/* Flex container makes buttons responsive */}
))}
)}
); }
